---
import { Layout } from "/layouts/layout.squirrel";
const title = "Create Project";
---
<Layout>
    <h1>${title}</h1>

    <p>
        To create a new project run following command in terminal.
    </p>

    <pre class="code" data-lang="Bash"><code>deno run http://denoland.com/x/squirrel/project/create.ts</code></pre>

    <h3>Setup Guide</h3>

    You will ask following question questions:

    <ol>
        <li>Choose folder for project</li>
        <li>Choose template for project</li>
        <li>Confirm Git init or not</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>After setup</h3>

    <pre class="code" data-lang="Bash"><code>cd {project-folder}
deno task start</pre>

    <a href="/getting_started/installation" class="btn btn-primary mr-2"><< Back</a>
    <a href="/getting_started/create_project" class="btn btn-primary">Next >></a>

</Layout>
